==發行==
電影於2016年9月1日在[[第73屆威尼斯影展|第73屆威尼斯影展]]上作全球首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-film-festival-unveils-lineup-915213|title=Venice Film Festival Unveils Lineup for 73rd Edition|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Alex|last=Ritman|date=2016-07-28|accessdate=2016-07-28|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011102431/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-film-festival-unveils-lineup-915213|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[華特迪士尼工作室電影|華特迪士尼工作室電影]]透過[[試金石影業|試金石影業]]排於2016年9月2日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Michael Fassbender-Alicia Vikander Drama ‘Light Between Oceans’ Gets September Release|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/michael-fassbender-alicia-vikander-light-between-oceans-1201701697/|accessdate=2016-02-10|work=Variety|date=2016-02-09|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126025228/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/michael-fassbender-alicia-vikander-light-between-oceans-1201701697/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=THRDist>{{cite news|author1=Pamela McClintock|author2=Gregg Kilday|title=Steven Spielberg, Jeff Skoll Team to Form Amblin Partners, Strike Distribution Deal With Universal|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/steven-spielberg-jeff-skoll-team-849249|accessdate=2015-12-22|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-12-16|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619085929/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/steven-spielberg-jeff-skoll-team-849249|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=DreamWorks Studios, Participant Media, Reliance Entertainment and Entertainment One Form Amblin Partners, a New Film, Television and Digital Content Creation Company|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20151216006049/en/DreamWorks-Studios-Participant-Media-Reliance-Entertainment-Entertainment|accessdate=2015-12-23|work=Business Wire|date=2015-12-16|location=Universal City, California|format=Press release|quote=Film projects in various stages of production include: “The BFG,” and “The Light Between Oceans,” scheduled for release by Disney in 2016.|archive-date=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223140533/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20151216006049/en/DreamWorks-Studios-Participant-Media-Reliance-Entertainment-Entertainment|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/the-light-between-oceans-michael-fassbender-alicia-vikander-derek-cianfrance-1201699550/|title=Oscar Bait Fassbender-Vikander Film ‘The Light Between Oceans’ Dated For Next Awards Season|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2016-02-09|accessdate=2016-02-10|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211171103/https://deadline.com/2016/02/the-light-between-oceans-michael-fassbender-alicia-vikander-derek-cianfrance-1201699550/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年10月7日於臺灣上映。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度58%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_light_between_oceans/ |title=The Light Between Oceans (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-09-02 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029004543/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_light_between_oceans |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分60<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-light-between-oceans|title=The Light Between Oceans reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-09-02|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327225005/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-light-between-oceans|dead-url=no}}</ref>，評價兩極，但以正面居多。主要稱讚電影仍保持原著扣人心弦的要素，以及演員的精彩演出。

===票房===
在美國，《為妳說的謊》於2016年9月2日上映，與《{{link-en|魔詭|Morgan (2016 film)}}》共同競爭。於首映週末預計能從一千五百間戲院中獲得600萬至900萬美元<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20160829-snap-story.html |title='Don't Breathe' likely to beat 'Light Between Oceans' and 'Morgan' in Labor Day box office |work=LosAngelesTimes.com |accessdate=2016-09-02 |archive-date=2018-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073118/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20160829-snap-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首映週末票房為500萬美元位居第六，口碑普通<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/dont-breathe-light-between-oceans-morgan-labor-day-weekend-box-office-1201812978/ |title=Don’t Breathe’ Still Has Oxygen, ‘Suicide Squad’ Seizes $300M+, ‘Morgan’ D.O.A. : Labor Day Weekend B.O. – Saturday Update |work=deadline.com |access-date=2016-09-06 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104233025/http://deadline.com/2016/09/dont-breathe-light-between-oceans-morgan-labor-day-weekend-box-office-1201812978/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

